Area served

Worldwide



Key people

Jan du Plessis, Chairman
Jean-Sebastien Jacques,[1] CEO


Products
Iron ore, Bauxite, Alumina, Aluminium, Copper, Molybdenum, Gold, Diamonds, Coal, Uranium, Titanium Dioxide, Borates, Salt, Talc


