Feedback























rio tinto marketing pte ltd
Private Company









Company Profile
Sector: Materials
Industry: Metals & Mining
Sub-Industry: Base Metals
RIO Tinto Alcan Pte. Ltd. provides metal products. The Company explores, mines, and processes bauxite, alumina, and aluminum products. RIO Tinto Alcan operates worldwide.




